These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, peas
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person eating peas##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | peas   | pineapple  |
| Sport   | snowboarding | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, artichoke
2 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the ferret is not the person eating artichoke##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | cucumber | artichoke      |
| Pet    | ferret  | turtle |

 #################################

 
