.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, funk
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, indian
1. the fan punk is on the far right##1
2. the fan funk is not the australian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | punk      |
| Nationality   | indian | australian |

