.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, paramedic
2 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the police-officer is not the owner of the ferret##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | police-officer | paramedic |
| Pet   | mouse       | ferret       |

