The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not the owner of the frog##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |
| Pet     | frog | hamster      |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | badminton |

 